    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Queen Slayer》是一款结构紧凑、节奏集中的Roguelike回合制RPG，2～3小时即可通关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从15名佣兵中挑选4人组队，对抗8位堕落女王的Boss战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有刷怪，没有重复战斗——每一场战斗都是Boss战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d39f458a5122a16d15e0148dfeb8ed0a.poster.avif?t=1770094622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d39f458a5122a16d15e0148dfeb8ed0a.webm?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d39f458a5122a16d15e0148dfeb8ed0a.mp4?t=1770094622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/d0fc153501f5ba5be5ee025ff5ecfbb3.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >短小精悍的战斗循环 – 2～3小时内通关</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss核心结构 – 每一战都直指8位堕落女王</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15名佣兵，4人小队 – 每轮都有不同策略组合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成长与抉择 – 简洁但有深度的成长系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单次游玩可完成全部成就<br>→ 所有与击败8位女王相关的成就都可在一轮内达成</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/f4047af1ec671cfec7beae6c1b474072.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每次选择，都是全新旅程</strong><br>即使是在短暂的游玩时间内，不同佣兵组合与策略变化也能带来全新的战斗体验。<br>快速通关后，也会想再次挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界已被堕落的女王吞噬。<br>毒素、冰霜、鲜血与钢铁覆盖了她们的领地，每位女王都有独特的战斗风格与视觉表现。<br>在这片黑暗而浓烈的幻想世界中，每一次行动、每一个决策都可能扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097380/extras/06fc1f7bce03c30bea2e9dc91f58b833.avif?t=1770094622\" width=800 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Queen Slayer》带来小而精的挑战。<br>探索回合制战斗与黑暗奇幻的魅力，找到属于你的战斗策略。</p>",
